The Nomination and Remuneration Committee has laid down the following criteria for performance evaluation of Independent Directors:
a) Attendance at Board meetings and Board Committee meetings;
b) Chairmanship of the Board and Board Committees;
c) Contribution and deployment of knowledge and expertise at the Board and Committee meetings;
d) Guidance and support provided to senior management of the Company outside the Board
meetings;
e) Independence of behavior and judgment;
f) Impact and influence; and
g) Performance of the Directors.

